title: 02/05/21 DPS Best OF
itunes:title: 02/05/21 DPS Best OF
description:
On Today's Dan Patrick Show, we wrap up Super Bowl week previewing the game with a couple Hall of Famers. Tony Dungy calls in to discuss what affect injuries will have on the Big game. Terry Bradshaw talks about his personality and why he is the way he is. And Nick Wright tells out why he thinks the Chiefs will win by 2 scores.
